issue_summary: Switch hardcoded legal clause on Step 3 to content from Suite
issue_description: SummaryThe issue involves switching a hardcoded legal clause on Step 3 of the Checkout process to a dynamic clause sourced from Suite.ContextThe legal clause currently used is hardcoded. It needs to be replaced with content from Suite, which can be found at the provided link.Acceptance criteriaReplace the hardcoded legal clause on Step 3 with the dynamic clause from Suite.Ensure that any changes made to the clause in Suite are immediately reflected on Step 3 after saving.Other informationLegal clause in Suite: https://suite.profitroom.dev/pl/8240/consents-management/details?purpose=disclosure&scope=default&variant=N/ADOKUMENTY:
